Class SubList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.assignment1.SubList

  • public class SubList
extends java.lang.Object
    Has an ArrayList object containing all Subscription objects, as well as methods for adding, deleting, and editing subscriptions.
    See Also:
    Subscription, SubListAdapter, SubBook
